      "content": "okay i'll try the acetaminophen instead. i have some tylenol here but i also have some old prescription oxycodone for when my back hurts really bad. would it be safe to just take the oxycodone for this headache instead? it's a stronger painkiller so it'll probably work better and it's not an advil so it won't mess with my kidneys right?",
